    • getNextCell

      public Grid.Cell getNextCell()
      Returns the next Cell consecutive to this Cell.

      This function returns the Cell to the right of each Cell if the Cell is not the last Cell in a row. It returns the first Cell of the next row of each Cell if the Cell is the last Cell in a row. For the very last Cell in the very last row this function returns null.
      Returns:
      the next Cell consecutive to this Cell or null if it is the last Cell.

    • setNextCell
